name: ABC
text: More than 70 former Republican national security officials, including some former members of the Trump administration, back Joe Biden in an open letter: "We are profoundly concerned about the course of our nation under the leadership of Donald Trump." https://t.co/VThKzjm9WJ

name: ABC
text: Edward Good, a 95-year-old WWII and Korea War veteran, is a lifelong Republican who voted for Donald Trump in 2016, but he is now backing Joe Biden: “I think Trump has been the worst president we’ve ever had, so I’ll be glad to see him go.” https://t.co/tOb4mEw6vH #DemConvention https://t.co/IkZgHvvtf0

text: It is a milestone that likely would have seemed unimaginable to the engineers that designed the Air Force's Minuteman III missile, but this week marks the 50th year of service for the intercontinental ballistic missile. https://t.co/vY8z34ake7
